<div id="fullPage">
	<div class="section">
		<div class="main-container">
	        <div class="main-row-1">
	          <h1>Unleash Your Creativity!</h1>
	        </div>
	        <div class="main-row-3">
	          <h2>JAMA Game Maker is a game creation tool that allows you to build, play, and share the game you've designed.</h2>
	        </div>
	        <div class="main-row-4">
	          <button class="btn-learnmore" onclick="fullpage_api.moveSectionDown();">▼</button>
	        </div>
    	</div>
	</div>
	<div class="section 2">
		<%=image_tag("gamecreator.PNG")%>
		<div class="main-container">
	        <div class="main-row-1">
	          <h1>1. Create your own game</h1>
	        </div>
	        <div class="main-row-3">
	          <h2>After clicking on the "create new game" tab, you will be able to create your very own turn based game after choosing a title, a description
	          	and a representing image. Then, you will need to create levels, events, assign events to levels, connect levels through doors and finally choose a starting level.</h2>
	        </div>
	        <div class="main-row-4">
	          <button class="btn-learnmore" onclick="fullpage_api.moveSectionDown();">▼</button>
	        </div>
    	</div>
	</div>
	<div class="section 3">
		<%=image_tag("gamecenter.PNG")%>
		<div class="main-container">
	        <div class="main-row-1">
	          <h1>3. Scroll through the collection!</h1>
	        </div>
	        <div class="main-row-3">
	          <h2>After clicking on the "game center" tab, you will see games you have previously created in the "your games" section and the other people's games in the "community games" section.</h2>
	        </div>
	        <div class="main-row-4">
	          <button class="btn-learnmore" onclick="fullpage_api.moveSectionDown();">▼</button>
	        </div>
    	</div>
	</div>
	<div class="section 4">
		<%=image_tag("gameplay.jpg")%>
		<div class="main-container">
	        <div class="main-row-1">
	          <h1>4. Play!</h1>
	        </div>
	        
	        <div class="main-row-3">
	          <h2>Let's see if you can clear this one, good luck! If you would like to discuss this game, you can do so in the "discussion" tab!</h2>
	        </div>
    	</div>
	</div>
</div>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/fullPage.js/3.0.8/fullpage.min.js"></script>
<script>
	new fullpage('#fullPage',{
		autoScrolling: true
	})
</script>
